flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{Filename argument present?}
    B -- No --> C[Print usage and exit]
    B -- Yes --> D[Strip path from filename]
    D --> E[Set username, server, and directory]
    E --> F[Read encrypted password file]
    F --> G[Decrypt password with cruft]
    G --> H[Open ftp session without auto-login]
    H --> I[Send username and password]
    I --> J[Switch to binary mode]
    J --> K[Change remote directory]
    K --> L[Upload file]
    L --> M[Close ftp session]
    M --> N[Exit]
